<template>
    <v-app id="inspire">
      <v-navigation-drawer v-model="drawer">
        <slot name="drawer"></slot>
      </v-navigation-drawer>
  
      <v-app-bar>
        <v-app-bar-nav-icon @click="drawer = !drawer"></v-app-bar-nav-icon>
  
        <v-toolbar-title>Application</v-toolbar-title>
      </v-app-bar>
  
      <v-main>
        <slot name="main"></slot>
        s
      </v-main>
    </v-app>
  </template>
  
  <script>
    export default {
      name:'NavBar',
      data: () => ({ drawer: false}),
    }

  </script>
